{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Steveostudios","author":"@steveostudios"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"e9a78bcd-edb5-5dde-afe3-95521189e250","excerpt":"We like to have a lot of fun in our youth ministry, and that usually means games. Throwing footballs through toilet seat covers, 300 student volleyball games…","html":"<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e9f6e013a8a0d352a27de05cf205367b/1cf84/score-keep-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 45.91836734693878%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Score Keep\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/e9f6e013a8a0d352a27de05cf205367b/4b3ab/score-keep-1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e9f6e013a8a0d352a27de05cf205367b/f8bb1/score-keep-1.jpg 148w,\n/static/e9f6e013a8a0d352a27de05cf205367b/900ac/score-keep-1.jpg 295w,\n/static/e9f6e013a8a0d352a27de05cf205367b/4b3ab/score-keep-1.jpg 590w,\n/static/e9f6e013a8a0d352a27de05cf205367b/78641/score-keep-1.jpg 885w,\n/static/e9f6e013a8a0d352a27de05cf205367b/1cf84/score-keep-1.jpg 980w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>We like to have a lot of fun in our youth ministry, and that usually means games. Throwing footballs through toilet seat covers, 300 student volleyball games, you know. But there has never been a good way to keep score, until now!</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/6d2eda57921d38ba5ae6dc6950ef6291/68866/score-keep-2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.1388888888889%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Edit Screen\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/6d2eda57921d38ba5ae6dc6950ef6291/6255c/score-keep-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/6d2eda57921d38ba5ae6dc6950ef6291/375dc/score-keep-2.png 148w,\n/static/6d2eda57921d38ba5ae6dc6950ef6291/6b157/score-keep-2.png 295w,\n/static/6d2eda57921d38ba5ae6dc6950ef6291/6255c/score-keep-2.png 590w,\n/static/6d2eda57921d38ba5ae6dc6950ef6291/68866/score-keep-2.png 720w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Like Spin That Wheel, Score Keep is made to be played on a single computer, PC or Mac, with the second display going out to a projector or TV on stage for large group interaction. You can customize the game by naming the game whatever you want, as well as your team names. If you want a count-down (or count-up) you can enable one and set the time. The Point Value is where you can set how many points are given at a time. You can even set whether a low score or high score wins (Auditorium Golf anyone?).</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a8fa519cedcc4690aa48423e1ebe2d3d/68866/score-keep-3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.1388888888889%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Play Screen\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/a8fa519cedcc4690aa48423e1ebe2d3d/6255c/score-keep-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a8fa519cedcc4690aa48423e1ebe2d3d/375dc/score-keep-3.png 148w,\n/static/a8fa519cedcc4690aa48423e1ebe2d3d/6b157/score-keep-3.png 295w,\n/static/a8fa519cedcc4690aa48423e1ebe2d3d/6255c/score-keep-3.png 590w,\n/static/a8fa519cedcc4690aa48423e1ebe2d3d/68866/score-keep-3.png 720w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>In the Play tab you can keep score with rapid fire clicks, or use the shortcut keys to add or minus points. You have basic countdown controls and when the game is officially over, have the game announce the winner!</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/8480251ca902fce25b2f0ac1f2c86882/68866/score-keep-4.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.1388888888889%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Themes Screen\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/8480251ca902fce25b2f0ac1f2c86882/6255c/score-keep-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/8480251ca902fce25b2f0ac1f2c86882/375dc/score-keep-4.png 148w,\n/static/8480251ca902fce25b2f0ac1f2c86882/6b157/score-keep-4.png 295w,\n/static/8480251ca902fce25b2f0ac1f2c86882/6255c/score-keep-4.png 590w,\n/static/8480251ca902fce25b2f0ac1f2c86882/68866/score-keep-4.png 720w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Finally, and this is in my mind the most exciting part, there are themes to make your game unique every time you play. Included are 10 themes to choose from (5 of which are Premium that can be unlocked after purchased from the website).</p>\n<p>You can save your Score Keep files for later use (make a game on Wednesday for Sunday’s use) or to share your game for other ministries to use on our Community Exchange page.</p>\n<p>Score Keep is available now here, for $25.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Score Keep","date":"September 02, 2011","tags":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/2011-09-02-score-keep/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/2011-07-11-lessons-in-yard-work/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Lessons in Yard Work"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/2011-09-08-apple-screen-sharing-bookmarks/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Apple Screen Sharing Bookmarks"}}}}